l\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-feedback\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-feedback\"></use></svg><span class=\"zDocsFeedbackButtonText\"> Feedback</span></span></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><button aria-label=\"Show topic actions\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" id=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-ellipsis-h\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-ellipsis-h\"></use></svg></button><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu zDocsTopicActionsMobileDropdown dropdown-menu-right\"></div></div><div style=\"flex-basis: 100%; height: 0px;\"></div><ul class=\"zDocsTopicPageDetails\"><li class=\"zDocsTopicPageDate css-cinqea\">Last Updated<span class=\"css-cinqea\">Nov 29, 2022</span></li><li class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryDetailsItem\"><button class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryButton\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-topic-summary\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-topic-summary\"></use></svg>Summarize</button></li><li class=\"spacer\" role=\"presentation\"></li><div class=\"zDocsLabelWrapper\"><ul><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: Uniface\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=prod_uniface\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>Uniface</a></li><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: 10.4\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=uniface_10.4\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>10.4</a></li></ul></div></ul></header><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBody\" data-prismjs-copy=\"Copy\" data-prismjs-copy-error=\"Copy failed! Use Ctrl + C instead.\" data-prismjs-copy-success=\"Copied!\"><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBodyContent wide\" dir=\"ltr\"><div id=\"zDocsAiSummaryContaineruniface_104cmy1665702748727.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/cmy1665702748727.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/cmy1665702748727.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"cmy1665702748727\" role=\"article\">\n<h1 class=\"title topictitle1\" id=\"ariaid-title1\">\n                 \n Grace Licenses\n </h1>\n<div class=\"body conbody\" id=\"cmy1665702748727__grace_licenses_204050\">\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"cmy1665702748727__p_d67406e1_d67407e1_d67408e1\">When using a network license, your Entitlement may give\n         you access to a grace period, known as a grace license. The grace period is determined by\n         the terms of your Entitlement.</p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"cmy1665702748727__p_d67409e1_d67410e1_d67411e1\">Grace licenses are only available on Windows and Linux.</p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"cmy1665702748727__p_d67412e1_d67413e1_d67414e1\">A grace license provides continuity in the case of an unforeseen emergency, such as a network or server outage or disconnection. This ensures that the application continues to run until the end of the grace period, allowing time for the issue to be resolved without causing a denial of service.</p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"cmy1665702748727__p_d67415e1_d67416e1_d67417e1\">A grace license does not need to be checked out; the application will have immediate access on the local system.</p>\n<div class=\"note note note_note\" id=\"cmy1665702748727__note_w1926ab1b3b9_w1927ab1b3_w1928ab1\"><span class=\"note__title\">Note:</span> \n                 Grace licenses are for emergencies. Should you need longer offline access, use a commuter license.</div>\n</div>\n</article></main></article>\n</div></div></div><div class=\"bottomFeedback\"><div aria-labelledby=\"bottomFeedbackText\" class=\"bottomFeedbackContent\" role=\"group\"><span class=\"bottomFeedbackText\" id=\"bottomFeedbackText\">Was this topic helpful?</span><div class=\"bottomFeedbackButtonGroup\"><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2526520\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-up\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-up\"></use></svg><span>Like</span></a><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2526520\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-down\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-down\"></use></svg><span>Dislike</span></a></div></div></div><div style=\"position: fixed; bottom: 170px; right: 70px; cursor: pointer; transition-duration: 0.2s; transition-timing-function: linear; transition-delay: 0s; z-index: 3; opacity: 0; visibility: hidden; transition-property: opacity, visibility;\"><button aria-label=\"Scroll to top\" class=\"zDocsScrollTopBtn\" data-tooltip-content=\"Scroll to top\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsBackToTopToolTip\" id=\"zDocsScrollToTop\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></button></div></body></html>", "text": "Grace Licenses Add to My Topics Add selected topic and subtopics Add Topic & Subtopics with topic head Add entire publication Watch Download PDF Save selected topic Save selected topic and subtopics Save entire publication Share Email Link Copy Link Feedback Last Updated Nov 29, 2022 Summarize Uniface 10.4 Grace Licenses When using a network license, your Entitlement may give you access to a grace period, known as a grace license. The grace period is determined by the terms of your Entitlement. Grace licenses are only available on Windows and Linux. A grace license provides continuity in the case of an unforeseen emergency, such as a network or server outage or disconnection. This ensures that the application continues to run until the end of the grace period, allowing time for the issue to be resolved without causing a denial of service. A grace license does not need to be checked out; the application will have immediate access on the local system. Note: Grace licenses are for emergencies. Should you need longer offline access, use a commuter license. Was this topic helpful? Like Dislike"}